summary: When do you think Tj started to like Cyrus or vice versa
question: When do you think Tj started to like Cyrus or vice versa
answer:
TJ started to like Cyrus pretty early on. Like he used a pick up line in swing scene 1.0, he’s been whipped for like the entire time he’s known him

Cyrus was later, he was a little scared at first and it took the time to warm up to him and Male a solid friendship, plus he was still hooked on Jonah for a while. It’s as he gets over Jonah he starts to realise feelings for TJ and I feel like that’s more known to Cyrus round Buffy in a Bottle when TJ teaches him a somersault, showing a real soft side to the boy who works in a kiddy gym. Before this he knows he enjoys being around TJ and doesn’t want to let him go but it’s not a fully realised crush yet, I mean he nearly lost buffy over keeping TJ in his life, and without buffy around he was free to properly come to love the basketball boy
